      • getArticles

        List<Article> getArticles()
        Gets a list of the Article returned as a result of HelpCenterService.searchArticles(String, String, String, String, String, Long, Long, Integer, Integer, retrofit.Callback)
        Returns:
        The list of articles. This will be an empty list if there were no results.

      • getCategories

        List<Category> getCategories()
        Gets a list of Category returned as a result of specifying 
        categories
        as a part of a sideload operation when calling HelpCenterService.searchArticles(String, String, String, String, String, Long, Long, Integer, Integer, retrofit.Callback) or HelpCenterService.listArticles(String, String, String, String, String, String, Integer, Integer, retrofit.Callback)
        Returns:
        The list of categories. This will be an empty list if there were no results or if categories were not side-loaded.
